Package views

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionsDialog
    Represents a dialog that allows the selected crew member to perform actions.
    ApplyMedicineDialog
    Represents a dialog that allows crew members to apply medical items.
    CreateCrewWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to choose and personalize crew members.
    CrewMemberWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to view each of the crew members' details and perform actions.
    EatFoodDialog
    Represents a dialog that allows a crew member to consume food items.
    GameOverWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to see their final score.
    InstructionsWindow
    Represents a window that explains the instructions of the game to the player.
    InventoryWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to view the details of each item in the inventory.
    MainWindow
    Represents the main window that allows players to play the game.
    OutpostWindow
    Represents a window object that allows players to purchase items.
    RepairShipDialog
    Represents a dialog that allows crew members to repair the ship.
    SearchPlanetDialog
    Represents a dialog that allows crew members to search the current planet.
    SelectPilotWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to select the pilots.
    SelectPlanetWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to select a new planet to pilot to.
    SetupWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to choose the game duration.
    SleepDialog
    Represents a dialog that allows crew members to sleep.
    StartingPlanetWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to select a starting planet.
    StartWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to start or quit the game.
